### Conventions and Patterns

- Agent `.md` first line must be `# Title` — the picker extracts it as the display label.
- Per-agent `.conf` fully replaces `default.conf` (no merging). Omitting `.conf` falls back to defaults.
- `default.conf` doubles as a reference of all supported Claude Code env vars (commented).
- Workspace must exist at `/ai_workspace` on the host (or be symlinked).
- No test suite. No git repo in the workspace.

